Author: tinycat1
Text: I feel this so much. Like today I was restricting and feeling like total trash and then someone asked for my number, and suddenly I’m on cloud nine like “yeah he thinks I’m hot cos I’m fuckin starving myself” fucking stupid Ed brain

Author: mqple
Text: unfortunately that’s just a symptom of ed. you ever notice how, even if you didn’t lose, you just feel thinner while restricting? i think it’s just a part of body dysmorphia. good luck though!
